  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the tagine pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the morning glory pak bung and cook until it is slightly wilted.",
    "Add the deep fry tod and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper, and stir well.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer the tagine for 10 minutes.",
